Q-1 --> 
make a rectangle and when we move mouse on the rectangle on the left side we want to gradually change the color of that rectangle to red and when we move mouse to the right side we want to change the color to blue .
Process:
1. check if mouse is in the rectangle and is it moving.
2. calculate if mouse cursor in left from center or right from center.
3. now calculate how much left we are from center & add red color based on that on that intencity.
4. now calculate how much left we are from center & add blue color based on that on that intencity.


Q - 2 -->
when we move mouse to the left side make the rectangle slow down the more mouse reaches to the left and do the same when mouse goes to the right side.